"And as proof, Morocco had four clubs in the semi-finals of the Champions League and the Caf Confederation Cup in 2020. A record that demonstrates the good organisation and balance of Botola's clubs.
"Moreover, the Moroccan championship dominates the ranking of the African championships of the CAF, including three clubs in the top 10."
"These three clubs - Raja, Wydad and Berkane, have won four major trophies in Africa in recent years: the Champions League, the CAF Cup (2) and the CAF Super Cup," the FRMF said.
'Infrastructure development'



